graph TD
    A[User Input + Execution Start] --> B[Environment Setup]
    
    subgraph Context Engineering
    B --> C[ChatPromptTemplate]
    C -->|Inject Variables| D[System Message: Context]
    C -->|Inject Query| E[Human Message: Goal]
    end
    
    subgraph LangSmith Telemetry (Invisible)
    D & E -->|Traced Payload| F[LangChain Chain]
    F -->|Raw LLM Call| G[OpenAI Model]
    G -->|Tokens & Latency Logged| F
    end
    
    F -->|Secure Async Logging| H[(LangSmith Cloud Dashboard)]
    F --> I[Formatted Output Return]
    
    I --> J[Application State Updated]
